description: "Vercel deployment and build rules"
pattern: "**/*"
rules:
  # Vercel Build Compatibility
  - Follow Next.js App Router patterns strictly
  - Ensure proper module imports/exports
  - Validate all file paths are case-sensitive
  - Check environment variable usage
  - Verify proper handling of dynamic imports
  - Follow serverless function format for API routes
  - Ensure proper usage of next/image and next/link
  
  # ESLint Compliance
  - Follow project ESLint configuration strictly
  - Avoid unused variables and imports
  - Use proper import ordering
  - Maintain consistent quote style (double quotes)
  - Follow proper naming conventions
  - Ensure proper prop-types usage in React
  - Avoid direct DOM manipulation
  - Use proper async/await patterns
  
  # Build Process
  - Verify all imports have corresponding dependencies
  - Ensure proper module resolution
  - Check for circular dependencies
  - Validate proper tree-shaking support
  - Verify correct usage of getStaticProps/getServerSideProps
  - Ensure proper middleware implementation 